<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="564" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1663,2014]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,1663,1689]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Pygofer, in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[570,656,1663,1689]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Fig. 28</figureCitation>
), subtrapezoidal, dorsoapical margin expanded dorsoposteriorly and curved ventrally at apex, inner caudal process (
<figureCitation box="[697,828,1699,1725]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Figs 28–29</figureCitation>
) adjacent to posterior margin and not surpassing the ventral margin, apex subtly bifurcated; subgenital plates, in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[985,1069,1735,1761]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
), slightly compressed on middle third, inner margin with about 20 teeth being larger and more sclerotized toward apex; aedeagus (
<figureCitation box="[1243,1371,1771,1798]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Figs 34–36</figureCitation>
) with pair of rounded lateral expansions in basal third with serrated margins, subapical processes very short, spine-like.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="567" pageId="5" pageNumber="564" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1663,2014]" box="[199,814,1843,1869]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,453,1843,1869]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Measurements (mm).</emphasis>
Male 
<typeStatus box="[525,627,1843,1869]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">holotype</typeStatus>
: total length 6.9.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1663,2014]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1879,1905]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Coloration.</emphasis>
Body yellow (
<figureCitation box="[498,600,1879,1906]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–6" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1830,1854]" captionTargetBox="[153,1404,189,1800]" captionTargetId="figure-25@2.[151,1435,181,1805]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–6. Habitus, dorsal and lateral views, respectively. 1 and 2, Rosalydia alvarengai gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. 3 and 4, R. inpa gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. 5 and 6, R. xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. Scale bars = 2.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964492" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964492/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Figs 5–6</figureCitation>
), green in life. Crown (
<figureCitation box="[856,921,1879,1906]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–6" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1830,1854]" captionTargetBox="[153,1404,189,1800]" captionTargetId="figure-25@2.[151,1435,181,1805]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–6. Habitus, dorsal and lateral views, respectively. 1 and 2, Rosalydia alvarengai gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. 3 and 4, R. inpa gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. 5 and 6, R. xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male. Scale bars = 2.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964492" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964492/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
) with four inconspicuous orange stripes, three longitudinal and one transverse forming E-shaped macula. Face (
<figureCitation box="[876,957,1915,1942]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Fig. 26</figureCitation>
) uniform yellow. Forewing (
<figureCitation box="[1278,1359,1915,1941]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
) semihyaline, anal margin and adjacent portion dark yellow.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1663,2014]" box="[199,1141,1987,2014]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,461,1987,2013]" pageId="5" pageNumber="564">External morphology.</emphasis>
External morphological characters as in generic description.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,150,897]" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,399,150,177]" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Male terminalia.</emphasis>
Pygofer, in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[688,772,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 28</figureCitation>
), subtrapezoidal, longer than high; ventral margin straight; dorsoapical margin expanded dorsoposteriorly, curved ventrally with acute apex; few short setae scattered apically; inner caudal process short and adjacent to posterior margin, not surpassing the ventral margin, in posterior view (
<figureCitation box="[160,247,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 29</figureCitation>
), curved inward, narrowing slightly towards apex, inner margin serrated on middle third, apex subtly bifurcated. Subgenital plate, in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[646,727,295,321]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 30</figureCitation>
) approximately 3.7 times longer than maximum height; wide at base and narrowing towards apex; apical half curved dorsally at an angle of approximately 135 degrees; in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[223,307,367,393]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
), each plate subrectangular, slightly compressed on middle third; inner margin with about 20 teeth on apical half, being larger and more sclerotized toward apex; apex acute. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[1127,1209,403,429]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 32</figureCitation>
) approximately half length of style. Aedeagus (
<figureCitation box="[448,576,439,466]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Figs 34–36</figureCitation>
) with pair of rounded lateral expansions in basal third with serrated margins; shaft slightly sinuous, tapered in apical two-thirds and laterally compressed in apical region; subapical processes very short; apex acutely rounded. Anal tube (
<figureCitation box="[656,737,511,537]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–36" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1818,1842]" captionTargetBox="[155,1424,189,1789]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[151,1436,181,1795]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–36. Rosalydia xavieri gen. et sp. nov., holotype male: 26, head, frontal view; 27, forewing; 28, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; 29, process of pygofer, caudal view; 30, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; 31, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 32, connective and style, dorsal view; 33, style, lateral view; 34, aedeagus, lateral view; 35, aedeagus, caudal view; 36, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars: 26 = 1.0 mm, 27 = 2.0 mm, 28–36 = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5964500" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5964500/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Fig. 28</figureCitation>
) with tergite X 2.5 times longer than wide.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,150,897]" box="[199,633,546,573]" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,425,546,573]" pageId="8" pageNumber="567">Female terminalia.</emphasis>
Female unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="567" type="materials_examined">
